Or even by filtering the data as

    UPDATE enchanttable_95_temp
    SET _State1Value = CAST(_State1Value AS NUMERIC(18,2)) / 1.10
                     -- SQL Server will cast the data to NVARCHAR here
    WHERE _State1Value NOT LIKE &#39;%[^0-9.]%&#39;;

